metadata.name: Sirens of Web3 #1
metadata.description:
"The Sirens of Web3" is a curated Ai collection which I created and then further edited within Photoshop/Lightroom. 

I'm completely new to Ai art generating but no stranger to capturing beauty from behind the lens, and being able to produce things I never thought possible simply by text has fascinated me completely.

Over time this collection will grow as I refine my outputs and I hope you enjoy my Ai journey.

Image Size: 1816 x 2310

https://linktr.ee/thephotograbber
